{
  "stem": "4189.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The, the beds, again, in there were like planks, four one on top of each other and four levels.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Again, four or five people were laying on one, on one bunk with no mattresses or anything, just some straw they had in there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were, of course, very sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They did not give us much food there, because the commandant of the camp there in Buchenwald said that the sick people don't need the full ration.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They only need the soup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They didn't give us any bread, because we are not productive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We cannot work, so we don't need the full ration.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So you can visualize our condition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In, In Buchenwald, there was a, there was a doctor, so-called doctor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We found out that he was really a butcher in private life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He was a butcher.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he was the surgeon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He did the operations in Buchenwald, in the, in that block 61.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "His name was Herman, incidentally.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He was a political prisoner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he did the best he could.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He amputated all the toes that were frozen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And some had to be legs amputated and whatever had to be done.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They had no bandages.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They had only paper.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They bandage it up with paper-- no medicine, nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Well, I was only a few weeks in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "When I arrived in Buchenwald in, in March, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on March 7th, I arrived in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And in April 11, the American Army advanced and liberated Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If it would have lasted a few day longer, few days more, I don't think I would have survived.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
